query:
SELECT b.id, b.name, b.totalNumbers, b.processedNumbers, b.status,
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM hlr_results WHERE hlr_results.batchId = b.id) as saved_results
FROM hlr_batches b 
ORDER BY b.id DESC 
LIMIT 10;
